      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. The chassis has been inspected for rear subframe fatigue, and the dual-VANOS system has been serviced to ensure precise cam phasing. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics, offering the communicative feedback and turn-in bite expected of the M-division's finest. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical integrity is robust, featuring a recently overhauled cooling system and preventative rod bearing replacement.",
